{"title":"山野的战歌","authors":["李瑛"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":11,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山野的战歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李瑛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨刺刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷一声，闪一道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山顶上磨刺刀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的汗，在刀身上淌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀的火，在我心头烧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫忘当年井冈险哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨哨都飞动红梭镖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫忘当年怒江急哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊涛骇浪洗大刀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今风雨三十载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天换了，地换了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只刀声未停人未老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀光下，走出咱一代新英豪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云滚滚呵歌滔滔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扳倒峭壁磨刺刀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨罢一掸铮铮响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山头上白光一道道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮头上红五星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮百里青山坳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的霜刃永不卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有胆的，刺刀尖上来报到！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过小河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨柳青，芦苇密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚霞落，炊烟起；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍柴回营过小河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见一群姐妹洗军衣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淙淙小河水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是否还记起？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十年前在这里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位老大娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为给子弟兵洗军衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被敌人害死在河心里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年战士听说这消息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不等伤愈要杀敌："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水洗战刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大山作磨石；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸药捆到薄雾起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦枪擦到夜鸡啼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舀一壶河水肩上背，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揣一腔烈火去出击！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自此后——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少战士上火线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少乡亲参军去；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云深雾重走兵马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四上枪声急……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自此后——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹树涛夜夜响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明月空照洗衣石；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捷报却恰似小河水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜流不息！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今不觉二十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十年风，二十年雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山变青呵水变绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青山栽柳柳荫浓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿水河边芦苇密；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今不觉二十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十年潮，二十年汐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷多少星月化成泥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只当年那块洗衣石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象是大娘一颗心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜跳动在山环里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青山不老人不老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代新人又站起；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿水不断歌不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耀眼的红旗照天地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士砍柴过小河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人激情似潮急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔节芦根细细嚼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘片柳叶吹柳笛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稍歇息，都记起——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是我们这群年轻人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年都生在那枪声里；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而你河边的好姐妹哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也定是那老大娘的亲儿女！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔一九六五年七月〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}